<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Development in Progress</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #f0f4f8;
            --accent-color: #6c5ce7;
            --text-color: #2d3436;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p {
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateY(0);}
            40% {transform: translateY(-20px);}
            60% {transform: translateY(-10px);}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">Under Construction</div>
        <div class="icon">🚧</div>
        <h1>開発中ページ</h1>
        <p>現在、新しい体験を準備しています。<br>公開まで今しばらくお待ちください。</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
